icks."}, {"version": "shield", "text": "During the day, it builds up energy via photosynthesis. At night, it flies silently through the sky, on the prowl for prey."}, {"version": "sun", "text": "This wary Pok\u00e9mon uses photosynthesis to store up energy during the day, while becoming active at night."}, {"version": "sword", "text": "At a distance, it launches its sharp feathers while flying about. If the enemy gets too close, Rowlet switches tactics and delivers vicious kicks."}, {"version": "ultra-moon", "text": "It feels relaxed in tight, dark places and has been known to use its Trainer\u2019s pocket or bag as a nest."}, {"version": "ultra-sun", "text": "It sends its feathers, which are as sharp as blades, flying in attack. Its legs are strong, so its kicks are also formidable."}], "entryGameVersions": ["legends-arceus", "moon", "shield", "sun", "sword", "ultra-moon", "ultra-sun"], "moveGameGroups": ["legends-arceus", "scarlet-violet", "sun-moon", "sword-shield", "ultra-sun-ultra-moon"], "evolutionRows": [{"stage": 1, "name": "rowlet"}, {"stage": 2, "name": "dartrix"}, {"stage": 3, "name": "decidueye"}]}